Package: ucLoader
Title: Unity Catalog File I/O Helpers for R on Databricks
Version: 1.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Mackenzie", "Ridout", email = "Mackenzie.Ridout@defra.gov.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Convenience helpers to access files stored in Databricks Unity
    Catalog Volumes from R. Supports listing directories, binary-safe downloads
    to local temporary paths, and binary-safe streaming uploads via the
    Databricks Files API, plus helpers to load/read common formats into an R
    environment. Supported formats include .qs2, .RData/.rda, .RDS, and .csv.
    Intended for RStudio Server on Databricks where the workspace URL and a
    personal access token are provided via environment variables
    (DATABRICKS_HOST, DATABRICKS_TOKEN). Does not require the /Volumes FUSE
    mount.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
